stockFeature.longBusinessSummary: InnovaQor, Inc. provides information technology solutions and services to healthcare and laboratory customers in the United States. It offers M2Select, which is an electronic health record and patient management software; M2Pro, a custom built, cloud based, electronic health record for ambulatory physician practices; ClinLab, which is a turnkey client/server lab information system for mid-range laboratories; Qira, a healthcare business analytics tool; MedTuning that provides clinical decision support for physicians and personalized drug treatment for patients; and Advantage, a proprietary health insurance portability and accountability act compliant software to eliminate the need for paper requisitions. The company also offers virtual chief information officer comprising program and project management, vendor management, business continuity and disaster recovery, security services, network infrastructure management, and helpdesk provision, as well as IT managed services and data analytics dashboards. In addition, it offers medical support services primarily to clinical laboratories, corporate operations, rural hospitals, physician practices, and behavioral health/substance abuse centers. The company is based in West Palm Beach, Florida.
